General.Name: Mulberry Group PLC
General.Description: Mulberry Group plc, together with its subsidiaries, designs and manufactures fashion accessories and clothing in the United Kingdom, Asia Pacific, and internationally. It provides briefcases, messenger bags, and backpacks; wallets, and purses and pouches; sunglasses, scarves, gloves and hats, belts, cufflinks, keyrings, and shoes; jewelry, organisers, leather care, and care products; gifts; and luggage, holdalls, bag, and other travel accessories for men and women, as well as ready-to-wear and eyewear products. The company sells its products through its retail shops, concessions, and wholesale distribution channels under the Mulberry brand, as well as sells its products online. Mulberry Group plc was founded in 1971 and is based in Bath, the United Kingdom. Mulberry Group plc is a subsidiary of Challice Limited.
